{"tid":1977132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不要對人透露自己的年齡","createTime":"2020-04-17T17:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T12:29:59.000Z","uid":47901,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9cbc4e36b73367919bafc34ea6b249c0f71daf","tid":1977132,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"一透露年紀，就產生危險性<br />\n<br />\n1: 如果對方年紀少過你，咁對方會話你係阿伯/阿婆， 會攻擊你腦根遲鈍，食古不化<br />\n<br />\n2: 如果對方年紀大過你，咁對方會話你入世未深，中二病，過份浪漫情懷<br />\n<br />\n結論:必輸(在這個香港社會)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上情況可以如此類推， 用以任何情況， 正反面必輸"},{"pid":"d4ae47d8fcf09a7f6e3927fd56f56fa8c507a964","tid":1977132,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"睇人"},{"pid":"72a0c930ef5d89aa81c122c304ede3d0680cef72","tid":1977132,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"問題係你唔講有人會起底，然後起錯底，或者作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終係芝麻風格，佢地諗住大話講多幾次就會變真"},{"pid":"0add5063f0cba865c91b7e9cce57fb27a6921342","tid":1977132,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"過埋五月就30歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e95dbf84c26157b31844881d9c45d89fad7a627","tid":1977132,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0add5063f0cba865c91b7e9cce57fb27a6921342","tid":1977132,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"過埋五月就30歲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"3999120a8ee935254c4efafc5306b10e4a94931b","tid":1977132,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0add5063f0cba865c91b7e9cce57fb27a6921342","tid":1977132,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"過埋五月就30歲了<img src=\"/assets/fac